Result.Data:
"The text topics object displays a set of words from a document collection, in this case Plot. The size of each term in the cloud indicates its importance. Text topics analyzes each value in the document collection as text containing multiple words. Text topics identifies words used throughout the document collection as relevant terms (omitting common words such as ""the""). It defines terms that appear together often in documents as topics.
With no selected topic, the word cloud displays the most common terms across the document collection. For example, ""life"" is the most frequently used term in this document collection."
